<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Buscar Cliente</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #128C7E;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        form {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #128C7E;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(18, 140, 126, 0.1);
        }

        button {
            padding: 14px 32px;
            font-size: 18px;
            background: #25D366;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #128C7E;
        }

        a.back {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #128C7E;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        a.back:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Buscar Cliente</h1>
        <p>Ingresa el nombre del cliente para ver su inventario, lavados y prendas dañadas.</p>

        <form method="POST" action="/dashboard">
            <input type="text" name="client" placeholder="Ej: Club Country" required autofocus />
            <button type="submit">Ver Dashboard</button>
        </form>

        <a href="/" class="back">← Volver al inicio</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>